### What is the purpose of the audio visual system?

The main purpose of an audio visual system is to facilitate effective communication by integrating audio and visual components. This system is designed to:

– Support dynamic presentations with visuals and audio.  
– Enhance learning and retention through multimedia content.  
– Foster better interaction during meetings, seminars, and events.  
